{"tid":675913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(特朗普又贏) NFL將祭「國歌法」， 球員不尊重國歌會令球隊挨罰","createTime":"2018-05-24T02:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T06:09:07.000Z","uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a2f056577f2b835bc863fad8fff7a5f17635418c","tid":675913,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:52:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180524/1359861/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180524%2F1359861%2F&d=24PkLJ6Ty%2FO0VFS1NGPvh54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=922a6129\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180524%2F1359861%2F&h=2ec75f22\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180524/1359861/</a><br />\n<br />\n針對去年美式足球員「跪國歌」風波，全國美式足球聯盟（NFL）周三宣佈新政策，凡出場的職球員在賽前奏國歌時不肅立，球隊將被罰款或受處分。球員工會表示，聯盟並未徵詢他們意見。<br />\n <br />\nNFL主席古德爾（Roger Goodell）表示，球隊老闆同意有關決定，又指球員有權選擇留在更衣室。<br />\n <br />\n不過，NFL球員工會指，聯盟沒有徵詢球員意見，若發現新政策有任何違反集體談判協議的細節，將提出反對。他們強調，球員跪國歌並非抗議國歌，只是對他們關心的議題表態。<br />\n <br />\nNFL球隊舊金山49人前四分衛卡帕歷克（Colin Kaepernick），前年在賽前奏國歌時不肅立，而是單膝下脆，以示抗議近年警察濫殺黑人等種族不公問題，其後有多名球員效法。總統川普去年炮轟「跪國歌」行為「不愛國」，引起掀然大波。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"66a475b68587a568951c8ebd0f2ab9504212f283","tid":675913,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:57:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37de63feb61ea7696505885f613c24ae3e0dac7c","tid":675913,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:24:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c724fcb9451e75fe4d7de463a9ced858a3f78d8f","tid":675913,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d4a7ad08ffd9e4044a981535f70efec575aa1a","tid":675913,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:26:55.000Z","msg":"到時又勞資糾紛NFL又要遲開季就好睇<br />\n又扯大纜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce83751e55b5934696fc09419612dab96dfb6f0","tid":675913,"uid":45368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T06:09:07.000Z","msg":"美國都搞國歌法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}